\n對應番5678既normally open<br />\n同9,10,11,12既normally close<br />\n<br />\n假設我做左個relay，剩係13,14駁左24V<br />\n呢個就係dry contact<br />\n<br />\n如果我除左13，14駁左，係24V source拉條正駁左common同NO/NC, 呢個就係24V contact"},{"pid":"ab33423f1672dadc8bea6b9f255577ecf4389af4","tid":1176184,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:44:52.000Z","msg":"可唔可以咁講<br />\nDry contact係一種用volt free電線黎交收digital signal(eg. NC/NO/ 同1/0) 既interfacing method。<br />\n<br />\n需然交收果條電線係volt free但係舊relay 要比電佢做交/收呢個動作<br />\n<br />\n有錯請教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34022013673b4ac54c75aca6f40dd108c66dfcc","tid":1176184,"uid":240533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"40d43499f47e98480d2123503a04b5f6499cca82","tid":1176184,"uid":256145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:41:23.000Z","msg":"究竟交個dry contact出去係乜野意思？<br />\n<br />\n上網睇咗好耐都唔明<br />\n<br />\n交dry contact同交24v個分別同作用係咩<br />\n<br />\n我問過師父 佢地淨係話24v係踢 dry contact係收<br />\n<br />\n越問越唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:44:57.000Z","msg":"Dry contact 即係你交出去毎個信號唔洗比電。純on/off 信號，個信號類似純碰埋2條線咁。<br />\n<br />\n交24V 即係交出去個信號有電，一般都會用黎控制relay. 比電relay 果2隻com 腳，咁隻relay 就會有動作。<br />\n<br />\n另外要更正一樣野，有野可以接dry contract ，自然都有野可以交dry contract。所以你要睇返個系統，唔好一味咁死記dry contact 就係收。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1950186c71fa2c4cff86a602001a2f27fce83816","tid":1176184,"uid":240533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ab33423f1672dadc8bea6b9f255577ecf4389af4","tid":1176184,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:44:52.000Z","msg":"可唔可以咁講<br />\nDry contact係一種用volt free電線黎交收digital signal(eg. NC/NO/ 同1/0) 既interfacing method。<br />\n<br />\n需然交收果條電線係volt free但係舊relay 要比電佢做交/收呢個動作<br />\n<br />\n有錯請教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:54:21.000Z","msg":"其實可以講深入少少，因為佢其實都係要行電，所謂既voltage free 只係交信號果邊（DO)唔洗比電個DI.<br />\n<br />\n而其實佢個signal circuit loop 既基礎都係行電，只係電由DI 內部個circuit 比埋出黎，最簡單係用transistor 做amplifier ，從而唔需要比個12/24V, 而可以用個勁細既current 都detect 到個status.<br />\n<br />\n由於DO果邊唔洗比錢，行業習慣既叫voltage free姐"},{"pid":"efcbfaae252f8c74290736b048753e392bcddd44","tid":1176184,"uid":47966,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:56:28.000Z","msg":"弱智都做到工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c15a6f04ddfa02a32ebe0d945a00f417459ec864","tid":1176184,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40d43499f47e98480d2123503a04b5f6499cca82","tid":1176184,"uid":256145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:41:23.000Z","msg":"究竟交個dry contact出去係乜野意思？<br />\n<br />\n上網睇咗好耐都唔明<br />\n<br />\n交dry contact同交24v個分別同作用係咩<br />\n<br />\n我問過師父 佢地淨係話24v係踢 dry contact係收<br />\n<br />\n越問越唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T06:05:04.000Z","msg":"點解唔問你大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cddbb6cb43531bfa3a90d53d6d88830ae94f82c","tid":1176184,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"交Dry contact=比張刀佢=個開關燈掣係你度，來電+燈都係對家果度<br />\n<br />\n交24V=你係盞燈，對家比LN你，但LN係由對家開關，L會冇電到<br />\n<br />\n有錯請屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd82a9146b2c4a94d970a95fe4c01b214f4e1bc","tid":1176184,"uid":256145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b12c9a6cab700a7861eeea3c15b0669b31ca836","tid":1176184,"uid":40250,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:11:56.000Z","msg":"Wet 有電<br />\nDry 無電<br />\n<br />\nRelay, 係一個俾電coil索contact既零件<br />\nRealy既13，14接點係coil既兩端<br />\n<br />\n1234係common<br />\n對應番5678既normally open<br />\n同9,10,11,12既normally close<br />\n<br />\n假設我做左個relay，剩係13,14駁左24V<br />\n呢個就係dry contact<br />\n<br />\n如果我除左13，14駁左，係24V source拉條正駁左common同NO/NC, 呢個就係24V contact"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:18:08.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打解釋得咁詳細<br />\n<br />\n姐係係咪消防仔交消防signal俾人，交dry contact就只係控制隻relay coil埋/彈<br />\n<br />\n交24v 就自己畀埋氣？ <br />\n<br />\n通常畀24v係咪只係踢警鐘/閃燈 唔會踢消防以外既野？"},{"pid":"33de4c780d68cb833ab09f6ce8639e082b1c5555","tid":1176184,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efcbfaae252f8c74290736b048753e392bcddd44","tid":1176184,"uid":47966,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:56:28.000Z","msg":"弱智都做到工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T03:33:53.000Z","msg":"依家d牛奶仔小小事都開post 問<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGoogle 下懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a799850562db6087717b1e2f1cc2f32007db2907","tid":1176184,"uid":167931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:35:13.000Z","msg":"你老味臭喺聽日同我去會計部計埋條數好執包袱走喇"},{"pid":"e508f260dfdadddecea849a3d0756a349baae209","tid":1176184,"uid":98795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:37:37.000Z","msg":"唔識就比人做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}